Cell monolayer graph generators¶

unit_hexagons[source]

unit_hexagons(Nx, Ny)

Produces hexagons with unit length edges, arranged in a hexagonal lattice.

vrn =unit_hexagons(10,10)

voronoi_plot_2d(vrn)
